#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid "Blocking"
msgstr "Blocage"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:251
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you plan to practice your vocabulary regularly, you should make sure "
#| "that the <emphasis>Blocking</emphasis> feature is enabled. The "
#| "<guilabel>Blocking</guilabel> options are part of the <link linkend="
#| "\"advanced-practice-configuration\">Advanced Practice Configuration</"
#| "link>. There you go to the blocking page and tick the checkbox that says "
#| "<guilabel>Blocking</guilabel>. Now you can even configure the interval in "
#| "which words that you answered correctly will be repeated."
msgid ""
"If you plan to practice your vocabulary regularly, you should make sure that "
"the <emphasis>Blocking</emphasis> feature is enabled. Go to the "
"<guilabel>Blocking</guilabel> page and tick the check box that says "
"<guilabel>Blocking</guilabel>. Now you can even configure the interval in "
"which words that you answered correctly will be repeated."
msgstr ""
"Si vous prévoyez d'exercer votre vocabulaire régulièrement, vous devriez "
"vous assurer que la fonctionnalité <emphasis>Blocage</emphasis> est activée. "
"Les options <guilabel>Blocage</guilabel> ont partie de la <link linkend="
"\"advanced-practice-configuration\">configuration avancée de l'exercice</"
"link>. Rendez vous sur la page de blocage et cochez la case qui indique "
"<guilabel>Blocage</guilabel>. Maintenant, vous pouvez même configurer "
"l'intervalle entre lequel les mots que vous répondez seront répétés."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Blocking</emphasis> means that words will not be asked for some "
"period of time after the last practice. This period of time depends on how "
"well you know the word, so that words you don't know yet will be asked more "
"frequently."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis>Blocage</emphasis> signifie que les mots ne seront pas redemandé "
"durant un certain temps après le dernier exercice. Cette période de temps "
"dépend de la façon dont vous connaissez ce mot, ainsi un mot que vous ne "
"connaissez pas encore vous sera demandé plus fréquemment."

